    <IsekaiLeveling.SkillTree.PassiveTreeDef>
        <defName>PassiveTree_Paladin</defName>
        <label>Paladin</label>
        <treeClass>Paladin</treeClass>
        <treeDescription>Unyielding guardians of the colony, Paladins turn punishment into power. Five constellations diverge from the paladin's core — each forging a different facet of their iron will. Absorb damage through the Sanctuary's Vow to unleash Divine Retribution on your next strike.</treeDescription>
        <classGimmick>DivineRetribution</classGimmick>
        <classGimmickName>Divine Retribution</classGimmickName>
        <classGimmickDescription>Every blow the Paladin endures is stored as retribution charge. The next outgoing melee strike releases that charge as a burst of bonus damage, then resets. Divine Retribution scales along the Sanctuary's Vow. Tier 1 (Saint's Guard): up to +15% bonus damage at full charge (50 dmg). Tier 2 (Iron Covenant): up to +30% (75 dmg). Tier 3 (Vow of Steel): up to +45% (100 dmg). Tier 4 (Holy Wrath): up to +60% (150 dmg). Charge is capped per tier — take hits, then retaliate.</classGimmickDescription>

